His blood was enough, and I acknowledge what He did for me.

00:19:33.378 --> 00:19:35.703
I do this often in remembrance.

00:19:35.703 --> 00:19:39.040
"Jesus, I thank you for what you did for me.

00:19:39.040 --> 00:19:42.879
" His blood was more than enough, and I just acknowledge it.

00:19:42.879 --> 00:19:44.080
"Thank you.

00:19:44.080 --> 00:19:48.571
Thank you, Lord, that you paid the price for me to walk in victory.

00:19:48.571 --> 00:19:51.280
" See, the coal has touched your lips.

00:19:51.280 --> 00:19:59.750
Now, your guilt is removed and your sins are forgiven.

00:19:59.760 --> 00:20:05.830
Who can the Lord send in these last days?

00:20:05.840 --> 00:20:09.919
You're more than enough because of His blood.

00:20:09.919 --> 00:20:20.320
Then I heard the Lord ask—He's asking tonight—"Who should I send as a messenger to the people?

00:20:20.320 --> 00:20:22.559
" I heard it today.

00:20:22.559 --> 00:20:24.940
I was driving around and I went around ORU again.

00:20:24.940 --> 00:20:33.039
I drove around again, sat out there and said, "Who can I send, Brandon?

00:20:33.039 --> 00:20:34.471
" I was not going to do a broadcast tonight.

00:20:34.471 --> 00:20:37.209
He said, "I want you to do one for me, please.

00:20:37.209 --> 00:20:39.760
" I said, "I will now.

00:20:39.760 --> 00:20:43.430
" Okay.

00:20:43.440 --> 00:20:52.480
Then I heard the Lord asking, "Who should I send as a messenger to this people?

00:20:52.480 --> 00:20:56.159
Who will go for us?

00:20:56.159 --> 00:21:00.177
" I said, "Here am I.

00:21:01.181 --> 00:21:03.190
Send me.

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:07.139
" I was driving and I was almost home, and I was turning around.

00:21:07.139 --> 00:21:09.503
I was going down and I was getting my kids something to eat.

00:21:09.503 --> 00:21:12.053
And I said, "Lord, it's over there.

00:21:12.978 --> 00:21:16.159
I'm trying to not go through the traffic.

00:21:16.159 --> 00:21:21.200
" He said, "It's not going to be convenient, everything I ask you to do.

00:21:21.200 --> 00:21:21.973
" I said, "Okay.

00:21:21.973 --> 00:21:29.360
" He said, "I want you to go over there, and I want you to sit, because you're thinking too small.

00:21:29.360 --> 00:21:33.463
I want you to sit in front of that Mabee Center because you're thinking too small.

00:21:33.463 --> 00:21:37.610
And remember the words that I've told you, that I'm bringing a revival to Tulsa.

00:21:37.610 --> 00:21:41.840
I'm going to bring a revival to the nations.

00:21:41.840 --> 00:21:43.488
You're thinking too small.

00:21:43.488 --> 00:21:44.640
You're thinking too poverty.

00:21:44.640 --> 00:21:46.799
You're thinking too little.

00:21:46.799 --> 00:21:48.857
Braden, look big.

00:21:48.857 --> 00:21:58.799
" And I remember across the school that it says in that auditorium, "Make no little plans here.

00:21:58.799 --> 00:22:17.209
" Oral Roberts had big on the inside of him, as I saw the big building and the medical center—they sold it now, but it was worth over $300 million, the building and all the stuff—and I was looking at all that he'd done whenever he was here, the campus, and I just sat there looking at it.

00:22:19.360 --> 00:22:20.178
And Diana and I...

00:22:20.382 --> 00:22:21.662
she goes, "Why are we here?

00:22:21.662 --> 00:22:28.960
" I said, "To get big on the inside of me, you got to get big on the inside of you.

00:22:28.960 --> 00:22:36.960
Start focusing on something other than your small world and realize that God wants us to reach the nations.

00:22:36.960 --> 00:22:41.600
Many, many people are dying and going to hell.

00:22:41.600 --> 00:22:46.090
And we limit ourselves in our own stinking thinking and think, 'Well, I'm not good enough.

00:22:46.090 --> 00:22:47.410
I have a past.

00:22:47.410 --> 00:22:50.159
' Who doesn't have a past?

00:22:50.159 --> 00:22:51.479
I'm talking to you.

00:22:51.479 --> 00:22:53.029
Who doesn't have a past?

00:22:53.029 --> 00:22:55.584
There's so many people that have a past.

00:22:55.584 --> 00:22:59.360
Your testimony is great.

00:22:59.360 --> 00:23:00.160
'Well, I did this.

00:23:00.160 --> 00:23:00.960
I got a divorce.

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:02.638
I had an abortion.

00:23:04.554 --> 00:23:07.110
God can't use me.

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:08.766
' But you're so mistaken.

00:23:08.766 --> 00:23:12.640
The blood is enough for you.

00:23:12.640 --> 00:23:16.320
The blood is enough for you tonight.

00:23:16.320 --> 00:23:23.440
There's no one that has too much sin in their life that God can't touch their lips with that blood, with that coal.

00:23:23.440 --> 00:23:30.080
He touched my lips with it and said, 'See, this coal has touched your lips.

00:23:30.080 --> 00:23:35.280
' The blood tonight, Jesus's sacrifice, touched your lips.

00:23:35.280 --> 00:23:42.240
Now your guilt is removed and your sins are forgiven.

00:23:42.240 --> 00:23:55.990
Then I heard the Lord ask, 'Whom should I send as a messenger?

00:23:56.000 --> 00:24:05.510
' I just believe it.

00:24:05.520 --> 00:24:08.799
We're in the last of the last days here.

00:24:08.799 --> 00:24:10.994
Jesus Christ is coming.

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:18.400
We're in the last of the last days here, and Jesus Christ is coming, and it's time for you to be all in.

00:24:18.400 --> 00:24:23.943
As I sat and I looked at that Mabee Center and I saw again—do you see the fire on top of the building?

00:24:23.943 --> 00:24:34.187
Do you see the glory that's about to be poured out over Tulsa, over Victory across the street with Paul Daugherty, and the glory?

00:24:34.187 --> 00:24:36.079
And he said this would be overflow.

00:24:36.079 --> 00:24:39.250
And I saw the old hotel that's closed down now.

00:24:39.250 --> 00:24:43.109
It has weeds all on the beds; it's all run down.

00:24:43.109 --> 00:24:45.140
This hotel across the street from the Mabee Center.

00:24:45.140 --> 00:24:47.960
And I sat there and just looked, and I thought, 'What would it take?

00:24:47.960 --> 00:24:51.279
' Because they're going to need something for the people to stay.

00:24:54.879 --> 00:24:55.279
There are going to be 24-hour-a-day services, seven days a week.

00:24:55.279 --> 00:24:57.348
There has got to be some place for these people to stay.

00:24:57.348 --> 00:25:03.440
There's a Marriott down the road on 71st Street on Lewis.

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:09.190
There's a Marriott, but that's not going to hold everybody.

00:25:09.200 --> 00:25:14.159
I thought, 'This is going to be something that we've never seen before.

00:25:14.159 --> 00:25:18.400
' I try to encourage you.

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:29.893
I remember whenever I was praying one night and I was interceding, and the Lord took me into the throne room, and I saw him sitting on his throne, and he came out.

00:25:29.893 --> 00:25:33.380
He was shielding himself because the light was so bright.

00:25:33.380 --> 00:25:36.347
I thought my eyes were going to burn out of my head.

00:25:36.347 --> 00:25:39.930
The vision, even in a vision, it was not natural.

00:25:39.930 --> 00:25:40.950
I wasn't really there.

00:25:40.950 --> 00:25:43.577
I think if I was really there, it would have killed me.

00:25:43.577 --> 00:25:46.376
That's how bright this was.

00:25:46.376 --> 00:25:49.896
But every single time, he has to shield himself.

00:25:49.896 --> 00:25:54.097
But it was so bright, it was so beautiful.

00:25:54.097 --> 00:25:58.720
He came out of it as a massive eye of fire.

00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:06.400
The fire was moving, and everything he said in the throne room, it became a seed.

00:26:06.400 --> 00:26:11.440
It was the size of a grain of a mustard seed.

00:26:11.440 --> 00:26:18.869
And the mustard seed grain, every word became alive, and they all joined together and started to form roots.

00:26:18.869 --> 00:26:20.640
They didn't die.

00:26:20.640 --> 00:26:43.800
His words became alive, and they formed all together, and they came as a seed, and the seed grew together, and the roots formed, and the sentences all lined up, and they all formed one massive, beautiful thing as they started drinking from a pool of water that was below.

00:26:43.800 --> 00:26:52.889
And it was ankle-deep, it was waist-deep, it was over, and I could see the water, and it was just pure as the eye could see.

00:26:52.889 --> 00:26:56.773
The water was as deep all the way at the beginning at the base of his throne.

00:26:56.773 --> 00:26:59.040
I could see this beautiful water.

00:26:59.040 --> 00:27:04.559
And he said, 'You must go down to the deep.

00:27:04.559 --> 00:27:08.799
You must go down to the deeper water.

00:27:08.799 --> 00:27:15.120
You used to abide there all the time, but over the course of time, you've gotten dry.

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:20.720
' And I was looking at that water, and I said, 'Lord, how do I get back in that?

00:27:20.720 --> 00:27:25.600
The cares of this world pull you out; you become dry.

00:27:25.600 --> 00:27:31.159
' And I could see the water, and it was the most beautiful pools of water.

00:27:31.159 --> 00:27:34.159
It was all different levels.

00:27:34.159 --> 00:27:39.200
There's levels of the glory; there's levels of his presence.

00:27:39.200 --> 00:27:54.533
But as I was looking at it, and I could see Pastor Tracy Harris from Texarkana, his prayers, and he allowed me—there were prayers that looked like comets that were burning around his throne, and they were shooting up like lights, and it was fast.

00:27:54.533 --> 00:28:02.239
They were coming up so fast, and they were burning up all around his throne, and he would breathe them in and he would breathe them out.

00:28:02.239 --> 00:28:08.106
I could hear him exhale and inhale the prayers of the saints, the prayers of the righteous, the people's prayers.

00:28:09.062 --> 00:28:10.950
They were coming up before his throne.

00:28:10.950 --> 00:28:13.806
And as he would inhale, he would inhale the prayers.

00:28:13.806 --> 00:28:15.748
And as he would exhale, they would come out.

00:28:15.748 --> 00:28:18.811
But they never died; they always were going around him.

00:28:18.811 --> 00:28:21.440
They were like balls of fire.

00:28:21.440 --> 00:28:26.063
And I saw one prayer—he paused it in front of me—and it was Texarkana.

00:28:26.063 --> 00:28:33.200
It was Pastor Tracy Harris, and he was praying for the nations.

00:28:33.200 --> 00:28:43.151
He was interceding for the last outpouring, and as that prayer came up before the throne, he was in the middle of the globe, and he was travailing for the globe.

00:28:43.415 --> 00:28:53.840
He was travailing for the souls, and the Lord said, 'From this day forward, there'll be an anointing that increases on this man's life.

00:28:53.840 --> 00:28:56.360
' And I saw another one.

00:28:56.360 --> 00:28:59.979
Then I had another dream, and the Lord keeps speaking to me about this man.

00:28:59.979 --> 00:29:05.279
I don't have any contact with this man, but I have had in the past.

00:29:05.279 --> 00:29:06.864
He came to the prayer conference, not recently.

00:29:10.444 --> 00:29:17.611
But the Lord said, 'I'm going to—it's time that there'll be four times the anointing and increase.

00:29:17.611 --> 00:29:18.622
' And I saw it.

00:29:18.622 --> 00:29:19.679
What did the Lord say?

00:29:19.679 --> 00:29:21.279
'Double.

00:29:21.279 --> 00:29:21.588
' Yeah.

00:29:21.588 --> 00:29:21.896
Double, double, double, double.

00:29:22.514 --> 00:29:24.480
But he said it now.

00:29:24.480 --> 00:29:26.559
Now, that's four times.

00:29:28.240 --> 00:29:30.640
Influence.

00:29:30.640 --> 00:29:41.029
I feel the anointing of the Holy Ghost all over me.

00:29:41.039 --> 00:29:53.039
But as I watched, he said, 'I've never created the church for escape.

00:29:53.039 --> 00:29:56.159
I created the church to have a backbone.

00:29:56.159 --> 00:30:02.846
I created the church—the armor was never designed for you to run and retreat.

00:30:02.846 --> 00:30:09.360
I only designed the armor for you to take dominion and authority and take the land for me.

00:30:09.360 --> 00:30:13.279
There was no armor on your backside.

00:30:13.279 --> 00:30:18.480
I don't want a church with an escape mentality.

00:30:18.480 --> 00:30:21.679
You occupy until I come.

00:30:21.679 --> 00:30:26.857
But I'm coming back for not a defeated church; I'm coming back for a glorious church.

00:30:26.857 --> 00:30:34.959
I'm coming back for a church that has a knowing of who they are, not a church that is in retreat mode.

00:30:34.959 --> 00:30:42.907
A church that is blood-bought, the church of the redeemed, people that are just saying, "Here am I, Lord.

00:30:42.907 --> 00:30:44.720
Send me.

00:30:44.720 --> 00:30:56.456
"' And he said to me again, "There's many of the elders, there's many of the—just like it was with the generation that had to go home because they wouldn't take the land.

00:30:56.456 --> 00:31:01.120
'We're the size of grasshoppers in their eyes; they're giants.

00:31:01.120 --> 00:31:02.948
The world is falling apart.

00:31:02.948 --> 00:31:04.840
We're not going to get it.

00:31:04.840 --> 00:31:11.817
' I'm looking for people, a new generation that will just say, 'Here am I, Lord.

00:31:11.817 --> 00:31:25.039
Send me'—the Davids, the Esthers, the Hannahs, or whoever—the young generation that has a backbone, that has no fear.

00:31:25.039 --> 00:31:28.731
If you're an elder and you say, 'Well, we're tired,' then the Lord said, 'It's okay.

00:31:28.731 --> 00:31:31.493
Help mentor some of these young people.

00:31:31.493 --> 00:31:41.142
Don't discourage them, but go ahead and tell them, "We are able to do, for there are many more with us than there are with them.

00:31:41.142 --> 00:31:43.200
" Either you believe it or you don't.

00:31:43.200 --> 00:31:46.391
If you don't, sit on the bench and get out of the way.

00:32:00.200 --> 00:32:00.640
" I died for every single one of them, Brandon.

00:32:00.640 --> 00:32:10.314
And he held his hands out, and I saw massive holes in his hands.

00:32:12.080 --> 00:32:22.847
"I wish that none should perish, but all come to repentance.

00:32:43.120 --> 00:32:43.493
" I saw those massive holes.

00:32:44.240 --> 00:32:46.471
I saw the harvest, and it was vast.

00:32:47.138 --> 00:32:49.447
And he said, "I'm sending my angel armies to help you.

00:32:49.447 --> 00:32:53.750
You're not doing this alone.

00:32:53.760 --> 00:33:07.280
" And I saw, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic spirit, I saw that Satan has blinded the eyes of the unbelievers like the Lord said.

00:33:08.570 --> 00:33:09.820
And he said, "Brandon, I'm going to assist.

00:33:24.129 --> 00:33:24.559
The blinders are coming off.

00:33:24.559 --> 00:33:34.640
They'll hear without being interrupted, for it doesn't matter how far or dark you think your relatives are.

00:33:34.640 --> 00:33:38.509
There's no way they'll ever serve Jesus.

00:33:38.509 --> 00:33:42.903
There is a way, and all things are possible to him who believes.

00:33:43.451 --> 00:33:45.519
" And I'm telling you, they're coming out of hell.

00:33:45.519 --> 00:33:49.840
They're going to come out of the hell they're living in.

00:34:03.291 --> 00:34:03.577
They're going to come out of this, and they're going to say, "I believe that Jesus Christ is going to be my Lord and my personal Savior as I confess my sins.

00:34:03.577 --> 00:34:07.770
He is faithful and just to forgive me of my sins and cleanse me of all unrighteousness.

00:34:10.377 --> 00:34:10.731
" I believe that today is the day of your salvation.

00:34:16.120 --> 00:34:16.509
I believe that there's no one too far gone.

00:34:24.079 --> 00:34:24.355
I believe that there's no one too sick that Jesus can heal.

00:34:38.651 --> 00:34:42.879
That's whenever I told you I saw the Valley of the Bones.

00:34:42.879 --> 00:34:48.960
And it was as far as the eye could see, and there were dead bones all over it.

00:34:48.960 --> 00:34:52.864
And I heard a loud voice coming out of it.

00:34:52.864 --> 00:34:55.143
I could see a light, and it was beautiful.

00:34:55.143 --> 00:35:01.750
And he said, "Can these bones live, Brandon?

00:35:01.760 --> 00:35:03.240
" I said, "Yes, Lord.

00:35:03.240 --> 00:35:09.280
" He yelled it again, "Can these bones live?

00:35:09.280 --> 00:35:16.390
How dead is dead, Brandon?

00:35:16.400 --> 00:35:19.920
Though you were dead, yet shall you live.

00:35:19.920 --> 00:35:23.691
" And I saw the bones; they started to become alive.

00:35:23.691 --> 00:35:30.780
And the flesh that was not there, the lungs, the heart, the blood started flowing through them.

00:35:30.780 --> 00:35:36.183
And I saw it coming from the foot up, and it was like a tornado going around them.

00:35:36.183 --> 00:35:42.160
And what was dead and decayed became alive again.

00:35:42.160 --> 00:35:48.933
And I said, "If you believe, all things are possible to him who believes.

00:35:48.933 --> 00:36:01.510
" He said to me, "If you believe, if you believe—how dead is dead, Brandon?

00:36:01.520 --> 00:36:05.258
" I said, "Dead is dead.

00:36:07.760 --> 00:36:13.119
" I thought in my mind, you can raise the dead if they still have blood in them.

00:36:13.119 --> 00:36:21.750
Maybe you could raise the dead if they're just a little cold.

00:36:21.760 --> 00:36:27.820
But how dead is dead, even the embalmed?

00:36:27.820 --> 00:36:33.680
It's time to believe God for what seemed to be impossible to be possible in your life.

00:36:33.680 --> 00:36:43.589
Tonight's your night for your expiration date for your unsaved loved ones, for your unsaved wife, your unsaved husband, your kids that are wayward, all of it.

00:36:43.589 --> 00:36:45.328
I believe that there's a turnaround.

00:36:45.328 --> 00:36:56.674
There's an expiration date for everything you're believing for, and nothing is impossible to him who believes.

00:36:56.674 --> 00:37:01.794
But it's going to take somebody other than just a prayer that sits by and says, "Well, we're praying for you.

00:37:01.794 --> 00:37:07.733
" No, you're going to witness to those like we saw Maldonado doing, as we saw Billy Burke doing this weekend.

00:37:07.733 --> 00:37:14.263
There are so many people that stretched out and were trying to help those who were lost, reaching out.

00:37:14.263 --> 00:37:16.480
And I believe a lot of people got born again.

00:37:16.480 --> 00:37:18.960
A lot of people got healed this weekend.

00:37:18.960 --> 00:37:24.310
But tonight's your night.

00:37:24.320 --> 00:37:25.757
Tonight's your night.

00:37:29.010 --> 00:37:34.720
He said, "I've come to save that which was lost.

00:37:34.720 --> 00:37:41.800
" So tonight, if you're here and you say, "Brandon, I've never asked Jesus Christ to be my Lord and personal Savior," tonight's your night.

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:46.432
You say, "Well, I've never ever had a touch from Jesus before.

00:37:46.432 --> 00:37:48.160
" Tonight's your night.

00:37:48.160 --> 00:37:58.279
Right there in your car, right there in your house, right there in your kitchen, wherever you're watching, even if you might be watching the day after, Jesus will visit you right where you are.

00:37:58.279 --> 00:38:00.080
He's no respecter of persons.

00:38:00.080 --> 00:38:09.079
And he's looking, his eyes are looking throughout the whole world right now because we are at the last of the last seconds here.

00:38:09.079 --> 00:38:15.040
And he's saying, "Will you just confess me as your Lord and Savior?

00:38:15.040 --> 00:38:16.160
" Tonight's your night.

00:38:16.160 --> 00:38:18.420
You say, "Well, Brandon, will you pray for me?

00:38:18.420 --> 00:38:19.520
" I would be happy to.

00:38:19.520 --> 00:38:23.950
But I want you to be bold in your decision tonight and tell us, "Tonight's my night.

00:38:23.950 --> 00:38:25.200
I want to be saved.

00:38:25.200 --> 00:38:25.867
Tonight's my night.

00:38:25.867 --> 00:38:26.756
I want to turn.

00:38:26.756 --> 00:38:28.768
I used to be on fire for God.

00:38:28.768 --> 00:38:32.062
I've heard a lot about him, but I don't know where I'm at with God.

00:38:32.062 --> 00:38:39.858
" If you want to be sure in your decision tonight, tell me, "Hey, I want to make sure I'm right with God.

00:38:39.858 --> 00:38:42.684
I know a lot about him, but I don't know if he knows me.

00:38:42.684 --> 00:38:51.599
" If you want to make sure he knows you, if you want to make sure that your name is written in that Lamb's Book of Life, tonight's your night.

00:38:51.599 --> 00:38:51.793
Tonight's your night.

00:38:52.182 --> 00:38:55.040
So, I want you just to repeat this prayer after me.

00:38:55.040 --> 00:38:59.770
Say, "Jesus, I believe you're the Son of God.

00:38:59.770 --> 00:39:03.919
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

00:39:03.919 --> 00:39:09.200
Jesus, as of tonight, I turn my back on the devil.

00:39:09.200 --> 00:39:11.200
I'll not serve him anymore.

00:39:11.200 --> 00:39:12.747
I'll not serve Buddha.

00:39:12.747 --> 00:39:14.240
I'll not serve Muhammad.

00:39:14.240 --> 00:39:18.560
I'll not serve any kind of false god.

00:39:18.560 --> 00:39:22.240
But tonight, I dedicate my life to you.

00:39:22.240 --> 00:39:26.320
I make you my Lord and personal Savior.

00:39:26.320 --> 00:39:30.480
There will be no other gods before me.

00:39:30.480 --> 00:39:34.720
You are my one and only God.

00:39:34.720 --> 00:39:35.880
I am that I am.

00:39:36.460 --> 00:39:39.893
I serve you, Jesus.

00:39:39.893 --> 00:39:42.560
I repent of my sins.

00:39:42.560 --> 00:39:45.800
